headline: GTA Online
subtitle: Get a GTA$1,000,000 Bonus
content:
Anybody who plays GTA Online at any point between now and November 18th will receive a special bonus infusion of GTA$, to the tune of GTA$1,000,000.

Come back between November 19th and 25th to claim your GTA$1M - just in time to give your finances a nice boost before the holidays.
